description:
In this episode I get a little obsessed with Kelp Farms and figure out how to make a fast one for the base. We also take care of my log shortages by setting up a remake of the S9 Tree Farm down in the Moss Pit. Then I tease my idea for a new rock shop called Rock Bottom.
